# Copy to .env.local for development overrides (gitignored by Vite convention).
#
# Backend host for the data connections (MQTT websocket :8083, streamer :8000).
# Unset, the dashboard targets the host it is served from — correct for the
# single-host install. Set it when running `npm run dev` on a different machine
# than the capture stack:
#VITE_VSCC_HOST=192.168.1.188
